Here are paste-ready photorealistic prompts you can use in Nano Banana (or similar image models). Pick one scene or mix details from two prompts.

Education
Prompt:
Photorealistic public high school classroom late morning, natural light through tall windows with partial blinds, teacher at interactive whiteboard gesturing toward a diagram (projected content blurred), students at grouped desks angled away from camera taking notes, backpacks and science kits on laminate floors, believable acoustic tile and bulletin board papers out of focus, documentary learning environment—not stock “perfect classroom” poster—no district logos readable, no faces toward camera.

Shot on full-frame DSLR, 85mm or 35mm, f/5.6–f/8 for clarity, Adobe neutral profile, minimal oversharpening, natural chromatic aberration, real-world imperfections, documentary editorial style.


